The paper discusses a prototype Spark execution engine that takes advantage of AWS Lambda to provide a pure pay-as-you-go cost model for analytical processing on big data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Databases (cs.DB), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories.
